      "releaseNotes": "Enhanced Reliability: Internal network requests now automatically retry through the active VPN tunnel if direct connection fails during startup.\nNew Speed Test Options: Measure node latency using TCP, ICMP (Ping), or Connection tests with customizable concurrency and timeout limits.\nPerformance Boost: Rewritten speed test engine runs checks in parallel, completing latency tests much faster.\nInterface Polishing: Refined slide-to-connect gesture animations and improved loading indicators.\nUnder-the-Hood Fixes: Resolved minor bugs related to subscription updates, user-agent headers, and routing stability.",
